  "title": "Legal Secretary (Part Time)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a part-time legal secretary to provide administrative and secretarial support. Salary willbe commensurate with experience.</p><p><u>General Roles & Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>General administrative duties</li><li>Data entry & filing (physical and electronic)</li><li>Assisting in preparation of correspondence & basic legal documents</li><li>Monitoring of deadlines and lawyers’ schedule</li><li>Preparing bills</li></ul><p><u>Requirements</u></p><ul><li>At least 1 to 2 years’ experience in a law firm</li><li>Good command of written and spoken English and Mandarin</li><li>Good working knowledge of Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint and Outlook softwareapplications is essential.                 </li><li>Meticulous, well-organised and can work well under time constraints. Must be prepared towork beyond office hours when required</li><li>Motivated, pro-active and able to work in a team</li><li>Able to work 2 to 3 days a week</li></ul><p>Interested applicants are invited to write in via email to jobs@hoandwee.com. Please note that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
